{"tid":1651543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪要去到當眾槍殺，香港人先會醒","createTime":"2019-10-13T11:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T17:45:27.000Z","uid":93986,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"dffb69c952725525d3c0e5bde98c3264d41c6315","tid":1651543,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:21:54.000Z","msg":"和理非會有用？<br />\n美國制裁會有用？"},{"pid":"c882e56866863a8443eac0a5a7e2ff6b53249d05","tid":1651543,"uid":301079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:23:39.000Z","msg":"勇武抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88554f587b7a072bea0f310eb932844e1f82c22a","tid":1651543,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:26:17.000Z","msg":"聽日繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警要新仔幫上頭及大陸武警嘅罪行頂罪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651133\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651133</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8b0222613ceb207d5f80c5451040faee5bd0920","tid":1651543,"uid":55851,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:36:13.000Z","msg":"香港建國沙盤推演：<br />\n<br />\n現時香港3萬警察，我地5個普通人夠殺1個全副武裝黑警。即係只需要15萬勇武衝出街大屠殺就可以穩勝。<br />\n<br />\n殺死所有黑警後，解放軍就會出動，廣州軍區兵力約25萬，人數不敵，但我地只需集中防守香港邊境同封阻運兵系統，再組山區遊擊隊突襲，實行毛澤東游擊戰術，不出三年已經可以擊潰廣州解放軍。<br />\n<br />\n之後輸出革命，反攻廣東省，奪大量土地建國，再同北約簽定協防協議，香港國正式成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f0ee5354033cacc485352f05902ac5b790895b","tid":1651543,"uid":83907,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"武器都唔拎出黎就想被槍殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf5126da40d6dc5f0175db6088b53ac6d4b5117","tid":1651543,"uid":266342,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:46:55.000Z","msg":"我嫌進化得太慢啦<br />\n呢啲一早應該要做啦<br />\n民意已經歸左邊㗎啦"},{"pid":"c684635d6d9d838d23f716f0aeae7e583f37f3ac","